T*
() Tj
T*
(Task 2 combines NLP and computer vision:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(the NER model extracts animal entities from text;) Tj
T*
(the image classifier predicts the animal shown in an image;) Tj
T*
(`pipeline.py` returns `True` if the image prediction matches one of the extracted) Tj
T*
(  animals, otherwise `False`.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(End-to-End Flow) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The complete pipeline follows this logic:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Prepare NER data with `Task 2/ner/prepare_data.py`.) Tj
T*
(Prepare image data with `Task 2/image_classification/prepare_data.py`.) Tj
T*
(Train the NER model with `Task 2/ner/train.py`.) Tj
T*
(Train the image classifier with `Task 2/image_classification/train.py`.) Tj
T*
(Run `Task 2/pipeline.py` with text, image, and both model directories.) Tj
T*
(The pipeline calls NER inference and image inference.) Tj
T*
(It compares the canonicalized animal names and returns a boolean.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Task 2 is therefore a composition task rather than a single-model task.) Tj
