(This is intentionally simple. The pipeline is not doing probabilistic reasoning or) Tj
T*
(ranking; it performs exact membership matching after normalization.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Pipeline Behavior in Edge Cases) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(If text contains multiple animals, the pipeline returns `True` if the image class) Tj
T*
(  matches any extracted one.) Tj
T*
(If NER extracts nothing, the result is `False`.) Tj
T*
(If the image model predicts the wrong class, the result is `False` even if the text is) Tj
T*
(  correct.) Tj
T*
